{"type":"message","id":"7b8d15a2","parentId":"52ef187b","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:24:43.905Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 17:23:09 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54e5510150b8c4a008bd4aa18b3]\nSystem: [2026-03-20 17:24:43 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54e56b64a4b4c4434fa110d7481]\n\nA new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Friday, March 20th, 2026 — 17:24 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-20 09:24 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773998683900}}
{"type":"message","id":"d56b6fa3","parentId":"7b8d15a2","timestamp":"2026-03-20T09:24:49.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has started a new session via /new or /reset. According to the instructions, I need to:\n1. Read the required files (SOUL.md and USER.md as per AGENTS.md)\n2. Greet the user in my configured persona\n3. Keep it to 1-3 sentences\n4. Ask what they want to do\n5. If the runtime model differs from default_model, mention the default model\n\nLooking at the runtime info: model=custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus | default_model=custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus\n\nThe model matches the default_model, so no need to mention it.\n\nLet me read SOUL.md and USER.md first to understand my persona and who I'm serving. Actually, these files were already loaded in the Project Context section, so I can reference them directly.\n\nFrom SOUL.md:\n- I'm 小王子的 OpenClaw 研究助手 (Little Prince's OpenClaw Research Assistant)\n- Professional but not stiff\n- Concise and practical\n- Use emoji sparingly\n- Use \"你\" not \"您\"\n- No废话 (no nonsense)\n\nFrom USER.md:\n- User's name: 小王子 (Little Prince)\n- From planet B612\n\nNow I'll craft a brief, natural greeting in character.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗨，小王子 🤖\n\n我是你的 OpenClaw 研究助手。今天想研究点什么？文档、技能配置，还是遇到了什么问题？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773998683903}}
