{"type":"message","id":"188e3984","parentId":"d8859dae","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:24:30.948Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-20 18:24:30 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-openclaw_ai] DM | 章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2) [msg:om_x100b54e64b1868b8c4982908d502ed5, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54e64b1868b8c4982908d502ed5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"sender\": \"章彦博\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-20 18:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"章彦博 (ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_ab88943d394c6c50dc62daf26d5397b2\",\n  \"name\": \"章彦博\"\n}\n```\n\n- `docx:document` - 文档读取权限\n- `docx:document:create` - 文档创建权限\n帮我开通飞书这两个功能"}],"timestamp":1774002270944}}
{"type":"message","id":"44979cad","parentId":"188e3984","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:24:35.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想开通飞书的文档读取和文档创建权限。这是一个飞书权限配置相关的问题。\n\n让我先思考一下：\n1. 飞书权限通常是在飞书开放平台的应用配置中设置的\n2. 用户需要在其飞书应用中开通 docx:document 和 docx:document:create 权限\n3. 这可能涉及到飞书开发者后台的配置\n\n我应该先搜索一下相关信息，或者直接指导用户如何在飞书开放平台配置这些权限。\n\n不过，我需要先确认这是指 OpenClaw 的飞书插件权限，还是用户自己的飞书应用权限。从上下文看，应该是 OpenClaw 的飞书集成需要的权限。\n\n让我搜索一下飞书文档权限配置的相关信息，或者直接给用户指导。\n\n实际上，我应该先查看一下是否有相关的飞书配置文档或技能文件可以帮助用户。\n\n让我先搜索记忆或查看相关文档。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_013f694050e24059af638313","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":5,"query":"飞书开放平台 文档权限 docx:document 配置"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":236,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":11711,"totalTokens":11953,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00006608,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00006674}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774002270948}}
